和沈寨镇中心小学没有强制要求学生订学生奶。目前，县教育局已经对这名老师进行了批评教育，并要求老师向家长道歉。https://cj.sina.cn/article/norm_detail?url=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2F2023-09-08%2Fdetail-imzkyxpy6885752.d.html&autocallup=no&isfromsina=yes"},"attached_info":"CkAIpJ/uz9n55JtYEAMaCTEwMDMzOTcwOCCxvfGnBjAAONMLQCRyCTYyMTI3MDA0MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"热度累计中","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b7089296485078ca7a8102d1eb53f835_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"37_1694358867.699436","card_id":"Q_60768638","target":{"id":60768638,"title":"与认知水平太低的人交流，是怎样的一种体验？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/60768638","type":"question","created":1496765966,"answer_count":129,"follower_count":519,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5357,7678,19882,21831,177663],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"你周围有认知水平极低的人吗？他们还要强迫你做一些明摆着很不明智的事情。我想每个人都有吧？你能给我们分享你的故事吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj4IpJ/uz9n55JtYEAMaCDE2NTMxMDM5II6s28kFMAA4hwRAJXIINjA3Njg2Mzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"热度累计中","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/6eefcddbd32650c1c757c30e70e6e8d7_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"38_1694358867.700751","card_id":"Q_25563003","target":{"id":25563003,"title":"为什么公文要用「仿宋_GB2312」字体？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/25563003","type":"question","created":1411888897,"answer_count":413,"follower_count":5959,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[261,270],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"现在都用着 WIN7/8，自带的仿宋和仿宋_GB2312有什么区别嘛？ 为什么大公司都规定必须用这个字体？"},"attached_info":"Cj0IpJ/uz9n55JtYEAMaBzI0MDc4NTUgge6eoQUwADjHLkA